%div.min-h-screen.bg-background
  / Hero Section
  %section.bg-gradient-to-r.from-blue-600.to-purple-700.text-white.py-20
    .max-w-7xl.mx-auto.px-4.sm:px-6.lg:px-8.text-center
      %h1.text-4xl.md:text-6xl.font-bold.mb-6 About WheelsOnRent
      %p.text-xl.mb-8.max-w-2xl.mx-auto
        Your trusted partner for premium car rentals in the UAE. We're committed to providing exceptional service and quality vehicles for all your transportation needs.

  / Mission & Vision Section
  %section.py-16.bg-white
    .max-w-7xl.mx-auto.px-4.sm:px-6.lg:px-8
      .grid.grid-cols-1.lg:grid-cols-2.gap-12.items-center
        .space-y-6
          %h2.text-3xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-6 Our Mission
          %p.text-lg.text-gray-600.mb-6
            At WheelsOnRent, we believe that everyone deserves access to reliable, high-quality transportation. Our mission is to provide seamless car rental experiences that empower our customers to explore, commute, and travel with confidence.
          %p.text-lg.text-gray-600
            We're committed to maintaining the highest standards of safety, customer service, and vehicle quality while making car rental accessible and convenient for both residents and tourists in the UAE.
        .bg-gradient-to-br.from-blue-50.to-indigo-100.rounded-2xl.p-8.shadow-lg
          .text-center
            %div.bg-blue-600.w-16.h-16.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-6
              %i.fa.fa-bullseye.text-white.text-2xl
            %h3.text-2xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Our Vision
            %p.text-gray-600
              To become the leading car rental platform in the UAE, known for innovation, reliability, and exceptional customer experiences.

  / Story Section
  %section.py-16.bg-gray-50
    .max-w-7xl.mx-auto.px-4.sm:px-6.lg:px-8
      .text-center.mb-12
        %h2.text-3xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Our Story
        %p.text-lg.text-gray-600.max-w-3xl.mx-auto
          Founded with a vision to revolutionize the car rental industry, WheelsOnRent has grown from a small startup to a trusted name in UAE transportation.
      
      .grid.grid-cols-1.md:grid-cols-3.gap-8
        .text-center
          .bg-white.rounded-xl.shadow-lg.p-8.h-full
            .bg-blue-100.w-16.h-16.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-6
              %i.fa.fa-rocket.text-blue-600.text-2xl
            %h3.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 2020
            %p.text-gray-600 Founded with a mission to simplify car rentals in the UAE
        .text-center
          .bg-white.rounded-xl.shadow-lg.p-8.h-full
            .bg-green-100.w-16.h-16.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-6
              %i.fa.fa-users.text-green-600.text-2xl
            %h3.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 2022
            %p.text-gray-600 Reached 10,000+ satisfied customers across the UAE
        .text-center
          .bg-white.rounded-xl.shadow-lg.p-8.h-full
            .bg-purple-100.w-16.h-16.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-6
              %i.fa.fa-star.text-purple-600.text-2xl
            %h3.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 2024
            %p.text-gray-600 Leading car rental platform with 500+ premium vehicles

  / Values Section
  %section.py-16.bg-white
    .max-w-7xl.mx-auto.px-4.sm:px-6.lg:px-8
      .text-center.mb-12
        %h2.text-3xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Our Core Values
        %p.text-lg.text-gray-600.max-w-3xl.mx-auto
          These principles guide everything we do and shape the way we serve our customers.
      
      .grid.grid-cols-1.md:grid-cols-2.lg:grid-cols-4.gap-8
        .text-center
          .bg-gradient-to-br.from-blue-50.to-blue-100.rounded-xl.p-6.h-full
            .bg-blue-600.w-12.h-12.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-4
              %i.fa.fa-shield-alt.text-white
            %h3.text-lg.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-2 Safety First
            %p.text-gray-600 We prioritize the safety of our customers and maintain the highest standards of vehicle maintenance.
        
        .text-center
          .bg-gradient-to-br.from-green-50.to-green-100.rounded-xl.p-6.h-full
            .bg-green-600.w-12.h-12.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-4
              %i.fa.fa-heart.text-white
            %h3.text-lg.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-2 Customer Focus
            %p.text-gray-600 Every decision we make is centered around providing the best possible experience for our customers.
        
        .text-center
          .bg-gradient-to-br.from-purple-50.to-purple-100.rounded-xl.p-6.h-full
            .bg-purple-600.w-12.h-12.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-4
              %i.fa.fa-handshake.text-white
            %h3.text-lg.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-2 Trust & Transparency
            %p.text-gray-600 We believe in building lasting relationships through honest, transparent communication and fair pricing.
        
        .text-center
          .bg-gradient-to-br.from-yellow-50.to-yellow-100.rounded-xl.p-6.h-full
            .bg-yellow-600.w-12.h-12.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-4
              %i.fa.fa-lightbulb.text-white
            %h3.text-lg.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-2 Innovation
            %p.text-gray-600 We continuously innovate to provide cutting-edge solutions and improve the car rental experience.

  / Team Section
  %section.py-16.bg-gray-50
    .max-w-7xl.mx-auto.px-4.sm:px-6.lg:px-8
      .text-center.mb-12
        %h2.text-3xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-4 Meet Our Team
        %p.text-lg.text-gray-600.max-w-3xl.mx-auto
          Our dedicated team of professionals is committed to providing you with the best car rental experience possible.
      
      .grid.grid-cols-1.md:grid-cols-3.gap-8
        .text-center
          .bg-white.rounded-xl.shadow-lg.p-8
            .w-24.h-24.bg-gradient-to-br.from-blue-500.to-blue-600.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-6
              %span.text-white.font-bold.text-2xl AH
            %h3.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-2 Ahmed Hassan
            %p.text-blue-600.font-semibold.mb-4 Chief Executive Officer
            %p.text-gray-600 15+ years of experience in the automotive and technology industries.
        
        .text-center
          .bg-white.rounded-xl.shadow-lg.p-8
            .w-24.h-24.bg-gradient-to-br.from-green-500.to-green-600.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-6
              %span.text-white.font-bold.text-2xl SM
            %h3.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-2 Sarah Mohammed
            %p.text-green-600.font-semibold.mb-4 Chief Operations Officer
            %p.text-gray-600 Expert in operations management and customer experience optimization.
        
        .text-center
          .bg-white.rounded-xl.shadow-lg.p-8
            .w-24.h-24.bg-gradient-to-br.from-purple-500.to-purple-600.rounded-full.flex.items-center.justify-center.mx-auto.mb-6
              %span.text-white.font-bold.text-2xl MK
            %h3.text-xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-2 Mohammed Khalil
            %p.text-purple-600.font-semibold.mb-4 Chief Technology Officer
            %p.text-gray-600 Leading our digital transformation and platform development.

  / Stats Section
  %section.py-16.bg-blue-600.text-white
    .max-w-7xl.mx-auto.px-4.sm:px-6.lg:px-8
      .grid.grid-cols-2.md:grid-cols-4.gap-8.text-center
        .space-y-2
          %div.text-4xl.md:text-5xl.font-bold 50,000+
          %div.text-blue-200.font-medium Happy Customers
        .space-y-2
          %div.text-4xl.md:text-5xl.font-bold 500+
          %div.text-blue-200.font-medium Premium Vehicles
        .space-y-2
          %div.text-4xl.md:text-5xl.font-bold 25+
          %div.text-blue-200.font-medium Locations
        .space-y-2
          %div.text-4xl.md:text-5xl.font-bold 99.9%
          %div.text-blue-200.font-medium Customer Satisfaction

  / CTA Section
  %section.py-16.bg-white
    .max-w-4xl.mx-auto.px-4.sm:px-6.lg:px-8.text-center
      %h2.text-3xl.font-bold.text-gray-900.mb-6 Ready to Experience WheelsOnRent?
      %p.text-lg.text-gray-600.mb-8
        Join thousands of satisfied customers who trust us for their transportation needs.
      .flex.flex-col.sm:flex-row.gap-4.justify-center
        = link_to cars_path, class: 'inline-flex items-center px-8.py-4.bg-blue-600.text-white.font-semibold.rounded-lg.hover:bg-blue-700.transition-colors.shadow-lg.hover:shadow-xl' do
          %i.fa.fa-car.mr-2
          Browse Cars
        = link_to new_user_registration_path, class: 'inline-flex items-center px-8.py-4.bg-white.text-blue-600.font-semibold.rounded-lg.border-2.border-blue-600.hover:bg-blue-50.transition-colors.shadow-lg.hover:shadow-xl' do
          %i.fa.fa-user-plus.mr-2
          Sign Up Now

  / Footer
  %footer.bg-gray-800.text-white.py-12
    .max-w-7xl.mx-auto.px-4.sm:px-6.lg:px-8
      .grid.grid-cols-1.md:grid-cols-4.gap-8
        .mb-4
          .flex.items-center.mb-4
            %i.h-8.w-8.text-primary.mr-2.fa.fa-car
            %span.text-xl.font-bold WheelsOnRent
          %p.text-gray-300 Your trusted partner for car rentals.
        .mb-4
          %h4.font-semibold.mb-4 Quick Links
          %ul.space-y-2.text-gray-300
            %li= link_to 'Browse Cars', cars_path, class: 'hover:text-white'
            %li= link_to 'About Us', about_path, class: 'hover:text-white'
            %li= link_to 'Contact', '#', class: 'hover:text-white'
        .mb-4
          %h4.font-semibold.mb-4 Support
          %ul.space-y-2.text-gray-300
            %li= link_to 'Help Center', '#', class: 'hover:text-white'
            %li= link_to 'Terms of Service', '#', class: 'hover:text-white'
            %li= link_to 'Privacy Policy', '#', class: 'hover:text-white'
        .mb-4
          %h4.font-semibold.mb-4 Contact Info
          .space-y-2.text-gray-300
            %p 📞 1-800-WheelsOnRent
            %p 📧 support@wheelsonrent.com
            %p 📍 123 Rental Street, City, State 12345
      .border-t.border-gray-700.mt-8.pt-8.text-center.text-gray-300
        %p &copy; 2024 WheelsOnRent. All rights reserved. 